   Learn French in france

A CENTER OF EXCELLENCE

   Created in 1964, under the impulse of the Universities of
   Clermont-Ferrand and the city of Vichy, CAVILAM (Centre d’Approches
   Vivantes des Langues et des Médias) joined the international network of
   Alliance Française in 2012.

   An international reference center, our institution is world renowned
   for its action in pedagogical innovation. Each year, it welcomes more
   than 4000 interns and foreign students from over 120 nationalities in a
   warm atmosphere and on an exceptional site.

OUR STRENGTHS

     * The highest teaching standards (Qualité FLE award)
     * The school is open throughout the year
     * New courses begin each Monday
     * A city designed with people in mind
     * French lifestyle to promote language immersion
     * Readily available team on hand to help

